    "body": "I've figured out when dnd doesn't work: when the notebook is running in secure mode over https, with Chrome on Linux.  No idea why, but apparently Chrome doesn't like drag and drop when using https.  With firefox, it still works fine.\n\nThe reason why I think this is really critical is that drag and drop has proven to be finicky over time (I've had problems with it several times), and when it fails, it can leave you pretty much stranded.  A simple upload button does the job 100% of the time.  \n\nI seem to recall @rkern posted a while back a link to a prettier solution than the ugly toolkit-driven 'Open' button that we're trying to avoid.  Robert, could you refresh our memory here?\n"
  },
